24-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-lightly-wounded-in-car-crash/0000018f-1b34-d502-a5bf-fbf6ed7c0000</guid></item><item><title>解释：为什么本周以色列-加沙校园战争与其他几周不同？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-why-is-this-week-in-the-israel-gaza-campus-wars-different-from-all-other-weeks/0000018f-1a7d-d8a4-a5cf-fefd57e10000</link><description>哥伦比亚大学校长米努什·沙菲克本应在 12 月的国会听证会上发表讲话，但这对哈佛大学和宾夕法尼亚大学的校长来说是灾难性的。幸运的是，她出城了。回想起来，如果她愿意的话，今天的美国校园可能会有所不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 16:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-why-is-this-week-in-the-israel-gaza-campus-wars-different-from-all-other-weeks/0000018f-1a7d-d8a4-a5cf-fefd57e10000</guid></item><item><title>18岁以色列女子涉嫌恐怖刺伤受重伤；袭击者被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/18-year-old-israeli-woman-seriously-wounded-in-suspected-terror-stabbing-assailant-killed/0000018f-1b14-d502-a5bf-fbf61b7c0000</link><description>中区指挥官阿维·比顿表示，袭击者在逃跑时试图刺伤另一名妇女。他的亲戚和朋友证实他精神不稳定</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 16:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/18-year-old-israeli-woman-seriously-wounded-in-suspected-terror-stabbing-assailant-killed/0000018f-1b14-d502-a5bf-fbf61b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>国外的以色列厨师说道：“我们感受到了战争的影响”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-chefs-abroad-dish-it-out-the-reverberations-of-the-war-are-felt/0000018f-159b-da70-a7bf-7d9b3f940000</link><description>就在一年前，以色列美食还是国际烹饪界的热门话题。然而，自加沙战争爆发以来，即使是米其林星级厨师也开始隐藏自己的身份</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 13:49:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-chefs-abroad-dish-it-out-the-reverberations-of-the-war-are-felt/0000018f-159b-da70-a7bf-7d9b3f940000</guid></item><