k-observers-to-visit-detention-facilities-holding-hamas-militants/0000018f-19aa-d1f3-afcf-3bebc67e0000</link><description>据《国土报》报道，近几个月来，几位目击者称，拘留设施中的囚犯每天 24 小时受到束缚并蒙住眼睛。斯德泰曼拘留中心设立的野战医院的一名医生描述了可能违反法律的情况</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 10:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-allow-u-k-observers-to-visit-detention-facilities-holding-hamas-militants/0000018f-19aa-d1f3-afcf-3bebc67e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人被真主党从黎巴嫩发射的反坦克导弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-by-hezbollah-anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon/0000018f-1947-d0a5-abcf-3fff64b00000</link><description>受害人谢里夫·苏阿德 (Sharif Suad) 35 岁，来自拉斯艾因 (Ras al-Ein)，他开车在该地区上班时，他的卡车被撞了</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:39:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-by-hezbollah-anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon/0000018f-1947-d0a5-abcf-3fff64b00000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心联盟的终结，内塔尼亚胡因人质交易而倾向于拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/fearing-the-end-of-his-coalition-netanyahu-edges-toward-rafah-operation-over-hostage-deal/0000018f-169d-d2e1-a7df-17bf7a680000</link><description>拉法行动将危及人质，可能不会推翻哈马斯 ■ 政府支持针对人质家人的恐吓行动，但未能援助北部流离失所的人们 ■ 只要以色列攻击加沙，真主党的纳斯鲁拉就不会退缩</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/fearing-the-end-of-his-coalition-netanyahu-edges-toward-rafah-operation-over-hostage-deal/0000018f-169d-d2e1-a7df-17bf7a680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在拉法的行动可能决定与真主党的“信息战”是否会成为现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/gazas-rafah-may-decide-whether-israels-war-of-messages-with-hezbollah-becomes-real/0000018f-16bb-d361-a3ef-56fb20cf0000</link><description>以色列在加沙南部城市的军事行动可能会导致总部位于黎巴嫩的组织决定是